<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1020910-did-i-miss-a-connection-about-decker-and">Did I miss a connection about Decker and Brodie in When Will There Be Good News? I understand the connection of Decker and JoAnna, JoAnna and Brodie (at two different times) but I couldn&#39;t understand why Decker was in Brodie&#39;s (supposedly) flat in Covent Garden.</a>
