This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
     I think Decker found Brodie near to death (or possibly temporarily dead) in the train wreck, and swapped IDs. He needed a place to to go, so he went <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
     I think Decker found Brodie near to death (or possibly temporarily dead) in the train wreck, and swapped IDs. He needed a place to to go, so he went to Brodie's apartment. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
