              <span id="reviewTextContainer3451142381" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7346107797135093771">I nearly didn’t read this! It’s the third book in the Brodie series and I thought the first book was just ok, I bailed on the second book but I really enjoyed this one! Full of mystery, great characters (I want to adopt Reggie!!) and lots of action. This was good fun! </span>

          </span>
