    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3810974829" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11060670101378698122">I have not had the best reading month, so I had to bring out the big guns. And as always Kate Atkinson did not disappoint.<br/><br/>This is not your typical detective or crime series with a lone brooding detective that solves crime in an unconventional way. No Jackson Brodie is a hot mess, and he knows it. Ex-military, ex-police and ex-wives colour his past and his pavlovian response to people asking for help gets him dragged into situations he never asks for.<br/><br/>I just love the dry humor, the complex and thr</span>
  <span id="freeText11060670101378698122" style="display:none">I have not had the best reading month, so I had to bring out the big guns. And as always Kate Atkinson did not disappoint.<br /><br />This is not your typical detective or crime series with a lone brooding detective that solves crime in an unconventional way. No Jackson Brodie is a hot mess, and he knows it. Ex-military, ex-police and ex-wives colour his past and his pavlovian response to people asking for help gets him dragged into situations he never asks for.<br /><br />I just love the dry humor, the complex and three-dimensional characters and how the writing can get me out of any reading slump.<br /><br />There are only 2 more books in this series and I will hold onto them till the next reading emergency.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="11060670101378698122" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


